WEBVTT

00:01:13.879 --> 00:01:14.239
Chen Fan

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:15.239
Ruochu

00:01:22.239 --> 00:01:23.920
Ruochu, Ruochu

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:32.719
Wasn't I hit by a car?

00:01:34.359 --> 00:01:34.920
Where are the documents?

00:01:55.319 --> 00:01:57.000
Only the dead can keep secrets.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:01:58.480
You offended the Long Group.

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.920
Your family and loved ones will pay the price.

00:02:01.599 --> 00:02:02.200
Next...

00:02:02.439 --> 00:02:04.680
...we'll start with your little boyfriend, Chen Fan.

00:02:12.319 --> 00:02:13.319
Chen Fan is okay.

00:02:14.199 --> 00:02:14.960
That's great.

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.719
It's not too late to stay away from Chen Fan.

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:19.599
I can't drag him into my mess.

00:02:20.919 --> 00:02:21.960
I'm sorry.

00:02:22.919 --> 00:02:23.680
Chen Fan

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:28.680
Ruochu

00:02:33.439 --> 00:02:34.319
Let's break up.

00:02:58.319 --> 00:03:00.240
Ruochu! Su Ruochu!

00:03:00.639 --> 00:03:01.759
Su Ruochu, are you there?

00:03:02.439 --> 00:03:03.159
Ruochu!

00:03:04.680 --> 00:03:05.680
Su Ruochu!

00:03:08.039 --> 00:03:09.479
Who is that? Go to sleep!

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:10.759
Su Ruochu!

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:12.719
Su Ruochu!

00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:16.439
Keep shouting and I'll throw hot water on you!

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:18.319
Throw it! I'll keep shouting!

00:03:18.319 --> 00:03:19.280
Just leave already.

00:03:19.639 --> 00:03:20.199
Stop making noise!

00:03:20.199 --> 00:03:20.840
Su Ruochu!

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.520
We're trying to sleep!

00:03:22.639 --> 00:03:23.520
Su Ruochu!

00:03:25.479 --> 00:03:26.319
You're Chen Fan, right?

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:27.560
Su Ruochu says to stop shouting.

00:03:27.719 --> 00:03:28.560
She's not coming down.

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:30.479
I suggest you stop pestering her.

00:03:30.919 --> 00:03:31.800
Besides...

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:32.680
Besides what?

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:34.039
Besides, making a scene like this...

00:03:34.120 --> 00:03:35.240
...is humiliating for Ruochu.

00:03:35.479 --> 00:03:36.639
From now on, whenever she goes up or down the stairs,

00:03:36.639 --> 00:03:38.120
people will point and whisper.

00:03:38.800 --> 00:03:39.199
I didn't mean to.

00:03:39.199 --> 00:03:39.840
Just go, hurry.

00:03:50.680 --> 00:03:53.759
The car accident happened during my internship in 2004.

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:55.759
It's only 2001 now.

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:58.919
Who exactly wants to harm me?

00:04:08.280 --> 00:04:09.080
The Long Group.

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:13.039
Long Group established...

00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:16.759
...entered Yunhai...

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:24.480
I probably won't find anything in these public records.

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:25.879
Then the internal Archives Room...

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:28.000
...might hold some clues.

00:04:41.319 --> 00:04:42.199
Let me introduce a newcomer.

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:44.360
Our new colleague, Su Ruochu.

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:45.240
Let's welcome her.

00:04:45.519 --> 00:04:46.240
Hello everyone.

00:04:47.319 --> 00:04:48.000
Get back to work.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:48.600
Come with me.

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:52.160
This is your new desk.

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.439
Read these materials to familiarize yourself with the business.

00:04:55.439 --> 00:04:56.040
Okay.

00:04:56.439 --> 00:04:57.319
Um, excuse me.

00:04:57.639 --> 00:04:58.240
I wanted to ask...

00:04:58.240 --> 00:04:59.920
which floor is the Records Room on?

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:00.680
It's on the third floor.

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:02.920
But why do you ask?

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:05.319
I just want to familiarize myself with the company.

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.560
So I don't go to the wrong floor when delivering files.

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:09.199
Xiao Wang.

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:10.279
Come here a moment.

00:05:10.600 --> 00:05:11.360
Oh, okay.

00:05:13.759 --> 00:05:14.439
You get to work.

00:06:03.399 --> 00:06:04.920
Archives Room.

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:08.040
Where is the Archives Room?

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:17.560
Who's there?

00:06:34.439 --> 00:06:35.279
Brother Honghai

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:36.720
Is something the matter?

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:38.519
I heard from your mom

00:06:38.519 --> 00:06:39.839
that you're interning at Long Technologies.

00:06:40.279 --> 00:06:41.680
Why didn't you tell me such good news?

00:06:41.959 --> 00:06:43.360
Long Technologies has been

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:44.360
one of the top companies these past two years.

00:06:44.360 --> 00:06:45.120
Even I want to work there.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:47.199
Today is my first day at work too.

00:06:47.319 --> 00:06:47.920
First day, huh?

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:48.560
Yeah.

00:06:48.920 --> 00:06:49.879
Are you still at the company?

00:06:50.079 --> 00:06:50.639
Yes.

00:06:51.439 --> 00:06:52.600
But I'm getting off work soon.

00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:53.079
Tell you what,

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:53.800
wait for me for a bit.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.000
I happen to be handling something nearby.

00:06:56.279 --> 00:06:57.639
Let me drive you back to school, okay?

00:06:57.639 --> 00:06:58.439
It's raining right now.

00:06:58.439 --> 00:06:59.240
You can't get back easily anyway.

00:06:59.439 --> 00:07:00.439
No need, Brother Honghai.

00:07:00.519 --> 00:07:01.079
It's fine, listen to me.

00:07:01.079 --> 00:07:01.720
Wait for me.

00:07:01.839 --> 00:07:02.199
I'll be there in a bit.

00:07:04.480 --> 00:07:07.279
Ruochu, I will definitely win you back.

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:13.319
Hello, Boss Liu.

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:15.920
You're the new intern in Marketing, right?

00:07:16.199 --> 00:07:16.519
Yes.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:19.920
It's so late.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:21.279
Working overtime on your first day?

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:24.319
Isn't it raining outside today?

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:25.959
I'm waiting for a friend to pick me up.

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:31.319
Ruochu.

00:07:32.079 --> 00:07:32.720
Brother Honghai.

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:34.759
So you were waiting for your boyfriend.

00:07:34.879 --> 00:07:36.439
I won't keep you young lovebirds.

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:38.079
Um, this is my friend.

00:07:38.399 --> 00:07:39.240
Brother Honghai, this is...

00:07:39.240 --> 00:07:40.160
I know, I know.

00:07:40.839 --> 00:07:42.480
Manager Liu of Long Technologies.

00:07:42.480 --> 00:07:43.240
Hello, hello.

00:07:46.879 --> 00:07:47.560
You're so young,

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:49.480
yet you've led Long Technologies to become an industry leader.

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:50.639
It's truly admirable.

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:51.959
I actually often read

00:07:51.959 --> 00:07:53.480
the articles about you in the newspapers.

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:55.360
Actually, we can be considered peers.

00:07:55.519 --> 00:07:56.519
My friend and I previously

00:07:56.519 --> 00:07:58.120
worked on a website called DomainNet together.

00:07:58.199 --> 00:07:59.120
This is my business card.

00:08:01.800 --> 00:08:02.959
Zhou Honghai.

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:05.279
So you're the person behind DomainNet.

00:08:06.759 --> 00:08:08.199
Alright, I'll remember you.

00:08:08.879 --> 00:08:10.079
Um, Brother Honghai...

00:08:10.079 --> 00:08:12.279
also ran a computer school back in our hometown.

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:13.680
I got it.

00:08:13.879 --> 00:08:15.199
Come by the company again when you have a chance.

00:08:15.399 --> 00:08:16.439
Let's talk about that website of yours.

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:17.439
Sure, sure, sure.

00:08:17.560 --> 00:08:18.360
Xiao Su.

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:19.879
Remember, don't stay alone next time

00:08:20.279 --> 00:08:21.160
working overtime this late.

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:31.560
Long Technologies

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:33.320
Big leaders at big companies are different

00:08:33.639 --> 00:08:34.600
So approachable

00:08:34.840 --> 00:08:35.840
He even took my business card

00:08:35.840 --> 00:08:37.480
Do you know a lot about Long Technologies?

00:08:37.519 --> 00:08:38.240
Of course

00:08:38.720 --> 00:08:40.639
Long Technologies is backed by the Long Group

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.159
In the tech industry these past two years,

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:43.320
it's the fastest-rising company

00:08:44.440 --> 00:08:46.080
But you coming here for an internship...

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:47.200
didn't you know about it?

00:08:47.399 --> 00:08:49.039
Of course I know about it

00:08:50.759 --> 00:08:52.799
I'm actually surprised you're interning here

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:55.080
Didn't you spend all your time before

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.399
hanging out with that kid Chen Fan?

00:08:59.519 --> 00:09:00.240
I...

00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:04.159
We've already broken up

00:09:04.639 --> 00:09:06.080
Just don't mention him in front of me

00:09:06.759 --> 00:09:07.480
Broken up?

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:08.879
When did that happen?

00:09:08.879 --> 00:09:09.399
A couple of days ago

00:09:09.399 --> 00:09:10.559
Didn't he just celebrate your birthday?

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.679
I saw he posted photos on his profile

00:09:13.559 --> 00:09:14.360
That's all in the past

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:15.879
Anyway

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.279
from now on, don't mention

00:09:18.279 --> 00:09:19.279
Chen Fan in front of me

00:09:20.279 --> 00:09:23.039
Or I'm afraid I'll find it hard to let go again

00:09:23.679 --> 00:09:25.080
So

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:27.320
you came here to intern just to avoid him?

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:33.519
It's normal for young couples to break up and make up

00:09:33.799 --> 00:09:34.639
But

00:09:35.080 --> 00:09:36.480
why did you two break up?

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:37.440
Well...

00:09:38.919 --> 00:09:40.720
it's hard to explain in a few words

00:09:41.879 --> 00:09:42.840
Just don't ask

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:45.120
You wouldn't believe me if I told you anyway

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:46.919
Stop asking

00:09:47.159 --> 00:09:48.080
Fine, I won't ask

00:09:49.039 --> 00:09:50.440
But I think that kid Chen Fan

00:09:50.960 --> 00:09:52.279
won't give up that easily

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:55.039
I hope he can move on soon

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:57.559
After all

00:09:58.759 --> 00:10:00.960
only being apart is best for him

00:10:04.679 --> 00:10:06.519
I think, how about this

00:10:07.039 --> 00:10:09.360
If he keeps pestering you

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:11.320
just say the two of us are together

00:10:11.799 --> 00:10:12.799
Provoke him a bit

00:10:12.799 --> 00:10:14.480
We've known each other for so long anyway

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:15.200
it'd be normal, right?

00:10:16.399 --> 00:10:18.480
I'll figure out the future when it comes

00:10:20.519 --> 00:10:22.480
Then you definitely have to come to me

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:24.559
I'm your best candidate

00:10:27.159 --> 00:10:27.480
Let's go

00:10:27.639 --> 00:10:27.919
Let's go

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.039
By the way, Brother Honghai

00:10:34.799 --> 00:10:36.600
about my internship at the Long Group

00:10:37.039 --> 00:10:38.480
could you not tell Chen Fan?

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:40.879
Sure

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:42.679
Don't worry

00:10:43.279 --> 00:10:43.840
Okay

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:49.639
I'll head back now

00:10:49.879 --> 00:10:50.200
Yeah